Hi @kishaningithub, we already have an issue tracking this request at #21953. As such, I will close this issue as a duplicate, and if you want to track any updates you can follow the already existing issue.

Note, you can use the `moved` block to explicitly move resources out of instanced resources without creating them.

For example:

```hcl

// Previous configuration
resource "aws_s3_bucket" "this" {
  count  = var.require_bucket ? 1 : 0
}

// New configuration

resource "aws_s3_bucket" "this" {}

moved {
  from = aws_s3_bucket.this[0]
  to = aws_s3_bucket.this
}

``` 

That workaround should help you remove any `count` arguments you don't need anymore.

Thanks!
